These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: tram, bus, jet-ski, skateboard, roller, motorbike
There are 6 different favourite colors: green, black, grey, mauve, orange, white
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person who likes orange is between the person driving the motorbike and the person who likes green##2
5. the person who likes mauve is between the person who likes orange and the person who likes black##2
6. the person who likes green is the person driving the skateboard##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who likes green##1
8. the person who likes white is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
9. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Transport           | tram | bus | motorbike | roller | skateboard    | jet-ski  |
| Color   | white | black   | mauve       | orange        | green | grey |

