.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, chess, poker, snooker, go
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: orchid, balloon-flower, dahlia, begonia, amaryllis, tulip
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is between the person playing poker and the person playing mah-jongg##2
4. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
8. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Game   | backgammon | go | snooker | poker | chess | mah-jongg  |
| Flower           | tulip | amaryllis  | orchid | balloon-flower    | begonia  | dahlia |

