.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice, soy-milk, milk
House: gothic-revival, colonial, victorian, cottage, cape-cod, palace
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person drinking juice is the cape-cod house##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cottage house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking juice and the gothic-revival house##2
7. the colonial house is on the far left##1
8. the victorian house is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | mirinda | milk      | soy-milk | juice | lemonade      |
| House   | colonial    | palace  | gothic-revival | cottage   | cape-cod       | victorian |

