.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, snooker, poker, go, canasta
There are 6 different favourite colors: black, turquise, pink, blue, fuchsia, red
1. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person who likes red is the person playing domino##1
3. the person who likes black is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the person who likes red is on the far right##1
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
7. the person who likes pink is the person playing canasta##1
8. the person playing snooker is between the person playing poker and the person who likes red##2
9. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Game    | mah-jongg | canasta | go  | poker      | snooker | domino  |
| Color   | turquise  | pink    | blue | black | fuchsia | red |

