.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: superhero, sports, action, western, time-travel, animation
City: marseilles, miami, venice, edinburgh, new-york, rome
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching western movies##2
4. the person watching western movies is the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to new-york##2
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
9. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Movie-Genre       | animation | western | superhero | time-travel | action | sports |
| City   | venice | rome    | new-york  | marseilles    | edinburgh    | miami    |

