.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: turquise, amber, grey, fuchsia, blood-red, chestnut
There 6 different types of food: pomegranate, asparagus, onion, raspberry, pepper, kiwi
1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person eating kiwi is between the person eating pepper and the person eating pomegranate##2
4. the person who likes fuchsia is the person eating onion##1
5. the person who likes grey is between the person who likes amber and the person who likes blood-red##2
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
9. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Color           | fuchsia | chestnut | blood-red | grey | amber | turquise |
| Food   | onion   | raspberry   | asparagus         | pomegranate    | kiwi     | pepper     |

