.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: electronic, pop, jazz, folk, salsa, hip-hop
6 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, cat, ferret, guinea-pig, snake
 1. the fan hip-hop is the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is between the fan electronic and the owner of the snake##2
 3. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is the fan hip-hop##1
 5. the fan electronic is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is the fan hip-hop##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the fan pop is on the left of the fan folk##1
 9. the fan salsa is on the left of the fan pop##1
10. the fan folk is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | salsa  | pop | folk | hip-hop | jazz     |
| Pet   | dog | mouse | snake    | guinea-pig | ferret | cat |

