.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: golf, tennis, snowboarding, volleyball, rugby, parkour
The people use 6 different means of transport: roller, quad-bike, van, boat, jet-ski, bus
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is tennis##2
6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person driving the van##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person driving the roller##2
9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Sport   | snowboarding | parkour | volleyball   | golf | tennis | rugby |
| Transport           | roller  | boat   | van | quad-bike | bus       | jet-ski |

