 4. the pilot is on the far right##1
 5. the engineer is between the bartender and the person who's sport is entrepreneuring##2
 6. the architect is on the right of the musician##1
 7. the musician is on the right of the person who's sport is entrepreneuring##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is the musician##1
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the musician and the person who's sport is parkour##2
10. the person who's sport is sailing is the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
