.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, june, january, december, april, november
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, game, fonseca, baccarat, bolivar, bongani
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is the baccarat-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in december and the bongani-smoker##2
 5. the fonseca-smoker is between the bongani-smoker and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 6. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 8. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Birthday           | june      | december | january | july   | november  | april |
| Cigar   | baccarat | alhambra  | game             | bongani | fonseca | bolivar       |

