 1. the brazilian is on the left of the mexican##1
 2. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes blue and the canadian##2
 3. the person who likes blue is between the pakistani and the person who likes black##2
 4. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the pakistani##1
 5. the pakistani is between the person who likes yellow and the malaysian##2
 6. the german is the person who likes purple##1
 7. the pakistani is on the left of the canadian##1
 8. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 9. the mexican is on the right of the brazilian##1
10. the german is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Nationality   | german     | brazilian | mexican   | malaysian     | pakistani       | canadian       |
| Color    | purple | turquise   | black | blue | orange | yellow |

