.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cricket, swimming, biathlon, baseball, rugby, golf
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, july, august, february, november, march
 1. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Sport   | golf | rugby    | biathlon     | swimming      | baseball    | cricket |
| Birthday   | july | january | november | august | march | february  |

