4. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in january##2
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
